cdata.name: Quantler
cdata.desc:
Quantler is a software company based in the Netherlands. It provides the users with a set of tools to assist them to create and develop cryptocurrency investment products. Note that is the user who controls its own funds, Quantler does not offer investment management services.

The QUANT token is an Ethereum-based (ERC-20) cryptocurrency. It is the token that supports and fuels the platform as it is needed for the user to host a Quant Fund at Quantler.
